### ATAN2
The [angle](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Atan2) between the positive x-axis and the ray from the
origin to the point (x , y) in the Cartesian plane, expressed in radians.

```esql
ROW y=12.9, x=.6
| EVAL atan2=ATAN2(y, x)
```
